<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 06:18:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国需求疲软损害了奢侈品公司历峰集团的销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-says-quarterly-sales-up-1-constant-exchange-rates-2024-07-16/</link><description>该公司周二表示，奢侈品集团和卡地亚母公司历峰集团的销售额在截至 6 月份的三个月内几乎没有变化，因为中国需求的急剧下降给整体业绩蒙上了阴影，使其略低于预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:47:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-says-quarterly-sales-up-1-constant-exchange-rates-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>ASML订单有望受益AI芯片热潮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmls-order-book-expected-benefit-ai-chip-boom-2024-07-16/</link><description>计算机芯片制造商的顶级设备供应商 ASML 预计将在其新老板周三公布第二季度业绩时报告新订单大量涌入，因为客户扩大产能以满足人工智能芯片蓬勃发展的需求。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:06:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmls-order-book-expected-benefit-ai-chip-boom-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国平安通过可转换债券交易筹集 35 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-ping-an-raises-35-bln-convertible-bond-deal-2024-07-16/</link><description>中国平安保险周二表示，已通过发行可转换债券筹集了 35 亿美元资金。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:03:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-ping-an-raises-35-bln-convertible-bond-deal-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国力图一石激起千层浪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-tries-hit-more-birds-with-one-stone-property-rescue-push-2024-07-16/</link><description>在北京命令中国城市购买新竣工的公寓并将其转变为经济适用房后，他们采取的首要措施是公布扩大补贴资格的计划，并解决这一过程中的其他经济难题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 04:07:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-tries-hit-more-birds-with-one-stone-property-rescue-push-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>暴风雨继续袭击中国，小镇遭遇全年降雨量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beijing-shuts-train-lines-rain-arrives-chinas-north-2024-07-16/</link><description>随着今年夏天袭击南方的极端风暴转移到中部和北部省份，中国河南的一个小镇一天遭遇了近一年的降雨量。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:49:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beijing-shuts-train-lines-rain-arrives-chinas-north-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国拖累，亚洲（日本除外）下跌，日元再次下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-16/</link><description>日本以外的亚洲股市周二小幅走低，因投资者思考特朗普获胜对中国意味着什么，而日元则恢复下滑，促使官员在上周疑似干预后发出新的警告。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:24:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>美联储鲍威尔言论聚焦九月降息，美元波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-drifts-powell-comments-bring-september-rate-cut-focus-2024-07-16/</link><description>周二，在美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔发表讲话以及前总统唐纳德·特朗普连任的可能性上升之后，投资者权衡了9月份降息的理由，美元从五周低点小幅回落。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 01:47:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-drifts-powell-comments-bring-september-rate-cut-focus-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>由于对中国需求的担忧挥之不去，油价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-tick-down-worries-about-chinese-demand-2024-07-16/</link><description>由于担心中国经济放缓抑制需求，油价周二下跌，不过越来越多的人认为美联储将在 9 月份开始降息，从而限制了跌幅。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 00:27:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-tick-down-worries-about-chinese-demand-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国和英国需求疲软，Hugo Boss 下调全年销售预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hugo-boss-cuts-full-year-sales-guidance-over-weaker-demand-china-uk-2024-07-15/</link><description>由于全球消费者需求疲软，尤其是中国和英国等市场的消费者需求疲软，德国时装公司 Hugo Boss 周一将今年的销售指引下调至 42 亿欧元（45.8 亿美元）至 43.5 亿欧元之间。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 22:30:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hugo-boss-cuts-full-year-sales-guidance-over-weaker-demand-china-uk-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国苦难加深，美国曲线陡峭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-15/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 21:50:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>包括哈马斯和法塔赫在内的巴勒斯坦派系将于七月在中国举行会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/palestinian-factions-including-hamas-fatah-meet-china-july-2024-07-15/</link><description>两名哈马斯和法塔赫高级官员周一对路透表示，包括竞争对手哈马斯和法塔赫在内的巴勒斯坦派别将于 7 月在中国举行团结会谈，试图解决深刻的分歧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:50:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/palestinian-factions-including-hamas-fatah-meet-china-july-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>审计证实世界游泳协会没有对中国兴奋剂案件处理不当</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/world-aquatics-did-not-mishandle-chinese-doping-cases-confirms-audit-2024-07-15/</link><description>世界游泳协会对中国游泳运动员药检呈阳性的处理情况进行的审计得出的结论是，管理机构没有管理不善或隐瞒情况，同时提出了恢复运动员对反兴奋剂系统信心的建议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:20:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/world-aquatics-did-not-mishandle-chinese-doping-cases-confirms-audit-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>德国经济部在欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税的投票中投了弃权票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-economy-ministry-abstained-vote-eu-tariffs-china-made-evs-2024-07-15/</link><description>德国经济部表示，在欧盟委员会周一讨论是否对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税时尚未做出决定，这实际上证实了其在周一投票中的弃权票。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 17:51:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-economy-ministry-abstained-vote-eu-tariffs-china-made-evs-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>新华社报道，中国北方地区进入强降雨高度戒备状态</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-northern-region-high-alert-heavy-rainfall-xinhua-reports-2024-07-15/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社周一报道，中国当局已将北方地区置于暴雨高度戒备状态，并正在准备全面紧急措施以减轻影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 17:31:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-northern-region-high-alert-heavy-rainfall-xinhua-reports-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>独家：国会称白宫应披露俄罗斯是否与中国分享美国武器见解</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/white-house-should-disclose-whether-russia-sharing-us-weapons-insight-with-china-2024-07-15/</link><description>美国国会两党委员会周一敦促白宫披露俄罗斯是否与中国分享如何击败乌克兰战场上使用的美国武器的见解的细节。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 17:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/white-house-should-disclose-whether-russia-sharing-us-weapons-insight-with-china-2024-07-15/</guid></item></channel></rss>